{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"SVG 样式属性","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/Styling","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>SVG 样式属性是所有可以在任何 SVG 元素上指定以应用 CSS 样式效果的属性。</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"#attr-class\"><code>class</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"#attr-style\"><code>style</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"class\"><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/class\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">class (en-US)</a></code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      给一个元素分配一个类名称或者设置类名。它跟 HTML 中的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-class\"><code>class</code></a>属性具有同样的功能。\n      <em>Value</em>: 任何可用的 ID 字符; <em>Animatable</em>: <strong>Yes</strong>\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"style\"><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/style\">style</a></code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      它指定元素的样式信息。它跟 HTML 中 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-style\"><code>style</code></a>属性具有相同的功能。\n      <em>Value</em>:任何可用的 ID 字符; <em>Animatable</em>: <strong>No</strong>\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器支持","id":"浏览器支持","isH3":false,"query":"svg.attributes.style","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/Styling/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"浏览器支持","id":"浏览器支持"}],"summary":"SVG 样式属性是所有可以在任何 SVG 元素上指定以应用 CSS 样式效果的属性。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"SVG Styling Attributes","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Attributs SVG de style","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"SVG スタイル付け属性","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/styling","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/